1. *Želim* da ti pomognem. (I want to help you.)
2. *Želela* bih da se vratim kući. (I would like to go home.)
3. *Želeo* bih da imam vise vremena. (I wish I had more time.)
4. *Želim* da se što pre uspostavi mir. (I want peace to be established as soon as possible.)
5. *Želela* bih da ti dam nešto za poklon. (I would like to give you a present.)
6. *Želio* bih da znam više o tome. (I would like to know more about it.)